<p><a href="https://gitlab.gnome.org/GNOME/gnome-tour/-/merge_requests/51">Bilal has merged</a> the fresh new GNOME 41 Tour, giving new users a nice welcome to their OS. Instead of screenshots here&rsquo;s some sketches from the design phase not to spoil the experience. You&rsquo;ll be able to enjoy the Tour when GNOME releases in September.

